Roxane Mesquida https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roxane_Mesquida 0 Roxane Mesquida (born 1 October 1981) is a French-American actress and model based in Los Angeles. Mesquida grew up in Le Pradet, a little town located in southern France. Her mother, writer Françoise Mesquida, is French/Spanish and her father is Italian/American, but Mesquida never got to know him. Mesquida is fluent in English and French, and she also speaks Spanish, Italian and German. Roxane_Mesquida ( born_1_October_1981 ) is a_French-American_actress_and_model based in Los_Angeles .
